/uploads/getty_images/538053368/image_538053368.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">ZoltanGabor</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This article is part of a series that provides an ongoing analysis of the changes made to Fundsmith's 13F portfolio on a quarterly basis. It is based on their regulatory <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1569205/000152002324000040/0001520023-24-000040-index.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1569205/000152002324000040/0001520023-24-000040-index.htm\" target=\"_blank\">13F Form</a> filed on 11/14/2024. Please visit our </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/538053368/image_538053368.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741906-terry-smith-fundsmith-13f-portfolio-q3-2024-update", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 03:52:52"}, {"id": "4741901", "title": "Limbach Holdings: A Hidden Gem Discovered This Year", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1657566602/image_1657566602.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Two Construction Workers Working Together on an Apartment Renovation\" data-id=\"1657566602\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1657566602/image_1657566602.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1657566602/image_1657566602.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1657566602/image_1657566602.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1657566602/image_1657566602.jpg?io=gett