_images/1169870817/image_1169870817.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741898-simon-property-group-remains-a-valuable-investment", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 02:29:52"}, {"id": "4741902", "title": "Okta, Inc. 2025 Q3 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Okta, Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q3 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106011\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741902-okta-inc-2025-q3-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 02:03:32"}, {"id": "4741893", "title": "TMSL: Multi-Factor ETF Off To A Good Start", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Racers at start line on track\" data-id=\"77930917\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1153px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77930917/image_77930917.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-widt