/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">joecicak</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>December 3 ended up being a pretty bad day for shareholders of <strong>United States Steel Corporation</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/X\" title=\"United States Steel Corporation\">X</a></span>). Shares of the company fell over 8% after <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4357389-trump-again-vows-to-block-us-steel-sale-to-nippon-steel\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4357389-trump-again-vows-to-block-us-steel-sale-to-nippon-steel\" target=\"_blank\">news broke</a> over night that President-elect Donald Trump has reaffirmed his opposition</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184967527/image_184967527.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741891-united-states-steels-plunge-represents-a-great-buying-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 01:45:38"}, {"id": "4741886", "title": "Agios Pharmaceuticals: A Long Overdue Follow Up", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Life Science Investing\" data-id=\"155151969\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"715px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155151969/image_155151969.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.